ile app, either through Wi-Fi, Bluetooth or a smart home hub. The app helps the smart smoke detector track battery life and sends you notifications to replace the battery before it starts to chirp in the middle of the night. It also lets you monitor conditions in your home, hush false alarms and test your devices remotely. If something happens when you’re not home, you receive an alert on your smartphone.<br/><br/>Smart Home Compatibility<br/>Each smart smoke alarm in our comparison can be used as part of a larger smart home system. If you already have a smart hub in your home, make sure the smoke detector you buy is compatible. The best devices work with a variety of platforms like Nexia, Vera, Wink, Google Home, Apple HomeKit and more."]},"id":"c0d88dfa-2126-480b-98f9-f664e4a7bb1f","type":"text"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["<br/><strong>More Smart Home Guides:</strong>"]},"id":"6af0a4de-5c14-4cdb-ba2b-522951a81f05","type":"text"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.toptenreviews.com/best-smart-locks\">The Best Smart Door Locks</a>","<a href=\"http://www.toptenreviews.com/best-programmable-thermostats\">The Best Smart Thermostats</a>","<a href=\"http://www.toptenreviews.com/best-home-security-systems\">The Best Home Security Systems</a>","<a href=\"http://www.toptenreviews.com/best-security-cameras\">The Best Home Security Cameras</a>"],"type":"ul"},"id":"dea2f893-75f0-4215-98e1-b923c7c1fc45","type":"list"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"en_US_43_Review_16","url":"/best-smoke-detectors","authors":[{"email":"jcarlsen@toptenreviews.com","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-05T12:56:28Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-05T12:56:28Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"},{"email":"","slug":"danny-chadwick","url":"/author/danny-chadwick","dateCreated":"2019-04-05T12:56:28Z","name":"Danny Chadwick","dateModified":"2019-04-05T12:56:28Z","id":"DhF8Hg8QQde8MtLyq8X8JN","dateImported":null,"site